snippet.title: Astral Gunners - Steam Early Access Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to push your skills to the limit against an endless sea of bullets and evil robots in Astral Gunners. Choose from five different gunners to master in this horizontal shooter. With the ability to dodge, reflect, delete, and convert bullets you are more powerful than you might believe.

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/893900/Astral_Gunners/
Soundtrack: https://samisati.bandcamp.com/album/astral-gunners-original-soundtrack

Game developed by Sami Sati and Erick Sati
Trailer edited by Woody Crobar
